The paper deals with physical layer security in a multiuser MIMO system, which involves topics such as information theory (cs.IT), network infrastructure (cs.NI), cryptography (cs.CR), control systems (cs.SY), and multimedia (cs.MM). However, since the focus is on beamforming and channel estimation errors, cs.IT and cs.NI are the most likely categories.
